item.title: SeaMeet Release History
item.description: 06/06/2024 # New Features and Performance Optimization # Adjust the number of concurrent meetings supported by SeaMeet, update database frequency and sync speed, and implement error handling for re-join entries. Audio Download for Paid Users - Paid users can download audio files for meetings held after June 1st. Help Desk - SeaMeet users can chat with the support anytime for assistance. Contact Support - Users can book support sessions via Hubspot for help.
